                            <incipit><locus>1b</locus><!-- insert --> 
                                vitarāgāya namaḥ.
                                ajñāna timirāndhānāṃ jñānāṃ jana salākayā, netramūnmīlitaṃyena taṣmai śrī
                                guruve namḥ ||1|| praṇamya paramaṃ jyotiḥ, pañcāpi parameṣṭinaḥ, dikṣājñāna
                                guruścāpi mamopakṛtikārakān ||2|| vakṣyehaṃ Kalpasūtrasya vyakhāyānāni nava
                                sphutaṃ, sugamāni subodhāni nānāgranthanusārataḥ ||3|| Tathāhi - ina i kṣetre
                                aneka gaṇadhara saṃpūran śṛūtadhara matā vyākhāni karṇahāranūa haumpaṇi karatuṃ
                                ināṃehavau dṛāṣṭāṃta
                            </incipit>
                            
                            <explicit><locus>22[a/5]</locus><!-- insert --> 
                                samaṇe bhagavaṃ  mahāvire tinnāno vagayabhothā caisāmitta jāṇai caimāṇa na jāṇai |
                            </explicit>
                            
                            <colophon><locus></locus><!-- insert --> 
                                Gatha padhaakharamattāī ahiyaṃhiṇaṃ ca jaṃmae lihīyam
